  "options": [
    {
      "id": "retreat_into_safety",
      "text": "Never again",
      "description": "The cost of courage is too high.",
      "resultText": "You make a decision: no more heroics, no more risks, no more sticking your neck out. You build walls around yourself, develop excuses for why you can't help, perfect the art of self-preservation. The guilt is real, but so is the relief. You won't be hurt like that again. You won't fail like that again. You'll be safe. Small. Invisible. But safe.",
